[MOVIE-SHOTS] This three-scene image captures a whimsical and enchanting story involving a young girl and a golden frog. [SCENE-1] begins with a close-up shot of a young girl with long blonde hair, wearing a white headband, white sleeveless top, and gold hoop earrings. She sits on a grassy lawn on a serene campus, her expression a mix of surprise and delight. She holds a yellow pencil in her hand, eyes wide with astonishment, mouth agape, and body leaning forward in amazement. In front of her, a golden frog sits on a rock, a shiny gold coin resting on its tongue, while cherry blossom petals drift gently through the air, enhancing the magical atmosphere. [SCENE-2] transitions to a medium shot, revealing the girl now standing up, her posture more assertive. She holds the pencil outstretched towards the frog, her eyes focused intently. The frog remains seated on the rock, the gold coin still on its tongue, but its eyes follow the pencil's movement. The air around them is filled with more cherry blossom petals, intensifying the magical aura. [SCENE-3] shifts to a close-up shot of the girl's face, her expression now a blend of determination and curiosity. She extends the pencil even closer to the frog, her fingers gripping it tightly. The frog's eyes are wide open, seemingly intrigued by the pencil. The gold coin on its tongue glistens under the soft light, and the cherry blossom petals continue to swirl around them, creating a sense of anticipation and wonder.

Name the role(s) with random name(s) if necessary, and wrap the name(s) with "<" and ">". Ensure the entire description is cohesive, flows as one sentence, and remains within 512 words.
Each scene should be a shot visual description of a story paragraph, not the full story, and only output the visual elements within the shot at this moment.
Each SCENE should be a moment captured by the camera, not too long!!!
